The matter in parentheses at the ends of sections in this Code is for information
               only and is not a part of this Code. Citations to ordinances indicate only the source
               of such section, and the text may or may not be changed by this Code. Reference matter
               not in parentheses is for information only and is not a part of this Code.
               
            

               (Code 1993, Â§ 1-10)
